(6,'HIPAA','HIPAA',4,'<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">\r\n<p><b>SOMERSET EYE INSTITUTE, P.C.</b></p>\r\n<div>ACKNOWLEDGMENT FORM</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">I,{PATIENT FIRST NAME} {MIDDLE INITIAL} {LAST NAME}, acting as a (place &quot;x&quot; in&nbsp;appropriate designation) patient, patient&rsquo;s representative, relative, do hereby acknowledge that, prior to the day of the surgical procedure, I received and reviewed the following documents:</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 1in\"><span>&middot;{ X }<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Patients Rights and Responsibilities</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 1in\"><span>&middot;{ X }<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Informational Document on Advance Directives</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 1in\"><span>&middot;{ X }<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>A disclosure of financial interest in this facility from my physician&nbsp;(if applicable)</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">I also acknowledge receipt from Somerset Eye Institute, P.C. of a Notice of Privacy Practices.&nbsp;I do further acknowledge that the Patients Rights and Responsibilities and this facility&rsquo;s &nbsp;policies regarding Advance Directives were verbally explained to me by a representative of this facility, prior to the date of surgery, to my satisfaction.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.75in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">I further acknowledge that I have informed&nbsp;Somerset Eye Institute, P.C.. of the existence, if any, of instructi