(7,'Car Service Waiver','Car Service Waiver',5,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">THE MACKOOL EYE INSTITUTE, LLC also known as THE&nbsp;EYE INSTITUTE</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">WAIVER AND RELEASE OF LIABILITY</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">Due to the nature of my medical condition and the medical services I receive as a patient at The Mackool Eye Institute,&nbsp;LLC (the &ldquo;Institute&rdquo;) aka The Eye Institute, it is difficult or impossible for me to drive or take public transportation to and from the Institute to obtain such services. In addition, it may be necessary for someone to accompany me to and from the Institute. Therefore, the Institute has arranged for my transportation and for someone to accompany me if necessary to and from the Institute for the purpose of obtaining medical services.&nbsp;I hereby acknowledge that Dr.&nbsp;{SURGEON NAME}&nbsp;and the Institute are not in the business of providing transportation and that the car service used for transportation to and from the Institute is not related to or associated in any way with Dr.&nbsp;{SURGEON NAME}&nbsp;and/or the Institute.&nbsp;I hereby agree on behalf of myself and my personal representatives, heirs, next of kin, executors, administrators and/or assigns to forever release, waive, indemnify, defend, hold harmless and discharge Dr.&nbsp;{SURGEON NAME}&nbsp;and the Institute and its members, officers, managers, medical director, administrator, employees, volunteers, representatives, agents, attending surgeons and anesthesiologists from any and all claims, actions, causes of action, damages (direct, indirect or consequential), demands, liabilities or expenses whatsoever (including attorneys&rsquo; fees and court costs), either in law or in equity, arising out of, incident to, or in any manner occasioned by or in connection with my transportation to or from the Institute.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">I HAVE READ THIS WAIVER AND RELEASE, I UNDERSTAND IT, AND I AGREE TO BE BOUND BY IT.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">Signature:&nbsp;{SIGNATURE}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: {DATE}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">Print Name: {TEXTBOX_MEDIUM}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">If the individual being transported is under 18 years of age, a parent or guardian also must sign and date this form.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>\r\n<div