0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">Signature:&nbsp;{SIGNATURE}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: {DATE}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">Print Name: {TEXTBOX_MEDIUM}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt\">IMPORTANT: FORMS MUST BE FAXED TO 718-728-0770 BEFORE CAR SERVICE CAN BE ARRANGED.</span></b></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','true'),
(8,'Anesthesia Consent','Anesthesia Consent',7,'<p style=\"text-align: center\"><b>Information About Anesthesia And Your Discharge From The Mackool Eye Institute, LLC</b></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">An anesthesiologist will monitor your blood pressure, heart rate, breathing, etc. during your surgery.&nbsp;An intravenous catheter will be placed by the anesthesiologist and in most cases you will be given medication to reduce anxiety and keep your blood pressure and heart rate within a normal range for you.&nbsp;Only very small amounts of medication are given during your surgery, and the effect of these medications will be very brief.&nbsp;You will be discharged from the Institute when you are physically stable and free from any significant effects of the medications you have received.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">We recommend that, if at all possible, you be accompanied by a responsible adult who will escort you home from surgery.&nbsp;We realize that this is not possible for every patient, and if you are not able to have someone do this for you, you must understand that:</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You are not allowed to drive yourself home from surgery.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You are not allowed to take public transportation home from surgery by yourself.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">While the above does not guarantee that there could not be an accident, such as a fall, it reduces the likelihood of one.&nbsp;Elderly patients always have a greater risk of falling and we strongly advise that an escort be present to accompany you whenever possible.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -2.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 2.5in\">Date&nbsp;{DATE}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -2.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 2.5in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -2.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 2.5in\">Patient Name: {PATIENT FIRST NAME} {MIDDLE INITIAL} {LAST NAME}</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">Patient&rsquo;s Signature: {SIGNATURE}</div>','true'),
(9,'Cataract Consent ','Cataract Consent',1,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 12pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16pt\">The Mackool Eye Institute, LLC</span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 12pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 12pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">Consent for Cataract Extraction with Intraocular Lens Implant </span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">1.<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I hereby authorize&nbsp;{SURGEON&nbsp;NAME}&nbsp;at The Mackool Eye Institute, L.L.C., to treat the cataract (opaque area that has developed in the lens) in my {SITE}.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">2.<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">The tasks this individual is expected to perform include, but are not limited to:&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><br clear=\"all\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">Opening and/or closing of surgical site</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">Dissecting (cutting) tissue</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">Removing tissue </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">Inserting a medical device</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">Altering tissues</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\"><br clear=\"all\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 3pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 3pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">3.<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I also authorize the physician(s) to carry out such diagnostic procedures to administer such treatments, and to administer such drugs, transfusion and intravenous medication as may be deemed necessary.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 6pt 0in 0pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">4.<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">My physician has fully explained to me the purpose of the operation. I understand that this will be done by making an incision (cut) into my {SITE}.&nbsp;The cataract will be removed from that eye and an intraocular lens implant (artificial lens) may be placed into my eye in an attempt to restore vision.&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 6pt 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">5.<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I have also been informed of expected benefits and complications (from known and unknown causes), attendant discomforts and risks that may arise, during the procedure and the recuperation period, as well as possible alternatives to the proposed treatment, including no treatment.&nbsp;The risks include, but are not limited to:&nbsp;bleeding into the eye, infection, retinal detachment, macular edema (swelling in the retina), clouding of the cornea, inflammation, double vision, drooping of the eyelid, partial or total loss of vision or even loss of the eye, cardiac arrest, respiratory arrest, allergic reaction to medications, brain damage and death.&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 6pt 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">6.<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I consent to the photographing or videotaping of the operation or procedures to be performed, including appropriate portions of my body, for medical scientific or educational purposes, provided my identity is not revealed by the pictures or descriptive texts accompanying them.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 6pt 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">7.<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">For the purposes of advancing medical education, I also consent to the admittance of observers to the operating room.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">8.<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I have been given an opportunity to ask questions, and all of my questions have been answered fully and satisfactorily.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">9.<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I understand that during the course of the procedure unforeseen conditions may arise which necessitate procedures different from those contemplated.&nbsp;I therefore consent to the performance of additional operations and procedures that the above-named physician may consider necessary.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">10.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">Any tissues surgically removed may be examined and retained for medical, scientific or educational purposes and such tissues or parts may be disposed of in accordance with accustomed practices.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">11.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I acknowledge that no guarantees or assurances have been made to me concerning the results intended from the operation or procedure.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">12.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I understand that certain procedures require the services of an assistant surgeon, and I authorize Jacqueline Dauhajre, MD to utilize the services of an assistant should he decide that this is necessary during the procedure that I have authorized him to perform.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">13.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I confirm that I have read and fully understand the above information.&nbsp;All blank spaces have been completed prior to my signing.&nbsp;I have crossed out any paragraphs or words above that do not pertain to me.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">Patient Acceptance or Risk</span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 6pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I understand that it is not possible for my surgeon to inform of all of the possible risks of my surgery.&nbsp;I do certify that I was given the consent form to take home with me and consider its contents prior to the day of surgery.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">{SIGNATURE}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><font size=\"2\">Patient {TEXTBOX_XSMALL}/Guardian {TEXTBOX_XSMALL}*</font> </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">Print Name: {TEXTBOX_MEDIUM}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">Date/Time: {DATE} / {TEXTBOX_MEDIUM}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <u><br />\r\n</u>Relationship to Patient:&nbsp;{TEXTBOX_MEDIUM}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.1in 6pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">{SIGNATURE}<u> <br />\r\n</u>