.25in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 27pt 0pt 0.25in; text-autospace: ; vertical-align: baseline; punctuation-wrap: simple\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">*<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt\">The signature of the patient must be obtained unless the patient is a minor unable to give consent or otherwise lacks capacity.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: medium none; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-left: 0in; padding-right: 0in; margin-left: 0in; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; margin-right: 27pt; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt\">\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 0in; margin: 6pt 0in 0pt; padding-left: 0in; padding-right: 0in; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">I hereby certify that I have explained the nature, purpose, benefits, risks of, and alternatives to (including no treatment) the proposed operation, have offered to answer any questions and have fully answered all such questions.&nbsp;I believe that the patient/relative/guardian fully understands what I have explained and answered.&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 6pt 0in 6pt 0.2in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 6pt 0in 6pt 0.2in\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">Surgeon:{SURGEON NAME}, MD</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 6pt 0in 6pt 0.2in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 6pt 0in 6pt 0.2in\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">{Surgeon\'s Signature}&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 6pt 0in 6pt 0.2in\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{Witness Signature}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>&nbsp;</u></span></div>','true'