(11,'Patient Defibrillators Notification','Patient Defibrillators Notification',8,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;<b>Patient Information Regarding Implanted Defibrillators</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">Patients with and Internal Cardioverter Defibrilllator (ICD) have had the device implanted in order to treat possible life-threatening arrhythmias.&nbsp;For most non-ophthalmic surgical procedures, it is recommended that the ICD be turned off so that it will not discharge improperly due to electrical current that is sometimes used to cauterize blood vessels during surgery.&nbsp;During eye surgery, however, if any cautery is used, it is of the &ldquo;bipolar&rdquo; variety and no electrical current is transmitted to the ICD.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">The Department of Anesthesia at The Mackool Eye Institute therefore believes the safest approach for ICD patients during eye surgery is to leave the ICD functioning.&nbsp;If the patient should have a life-threatening arrhythmia during surgery, it would therefore be treated most quickly by the device.&nbsp;If the ICD were turned off, there would be both a longer time period before treatment by external defibrillation could be administered, and there would be a significant risk of damaging the ICD from the external current.&nbsp;Should this occur, a new ICD would need to be inserted.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">Lastly, while there may be a minuscule theoretical risk that the ultrasonic energy of the phacoemulsification machine used to remove a cataract could cause the ICD to discharge, this has never been reported to occur and over the past twenty years our anesthesia department has never seen such a problem (it is estimated that approximately 1,000 patients with an ICD underwent cataract removal by phacoemulsification during this time period).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b>In summary, while there may be a minuscule risk of undergoing eye surgery in the presence of an ICD which is active, we believe that the risk would be greater if the ICD device were turned off.&nbsp;We therefore do not turn off ICD devices during eye surgery at The Mackool Eye Institute</b>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -3.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 3.5in\">Lawrence Rabinowitz, M.D.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Richard J. Mackool, M.D.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -3.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 3.5in\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Director, Anesthesia Department&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Medical Director, The Mackool Eye Institute</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">______________________________________________________________________________</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b>I understand that IMPLANTABLE DEFIBRILLATORS AND CARDIOVERTERS present a risk of injury if they should become activated during my surgical procedure</b>, and should this occur, emergency admission would be necessary to the nearest hospital. I have been informed of the above risks and alternate treatment plans.&nbsp;Based upon the above information, I wish to proceed with the proposed surgery at The Mackool Eye Institute.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -4in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 4in\">{SIGNATURE}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -4in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 4in\">Patient&rsquo;s Signature&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -4in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 4in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -4in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 4in\">{DATE}</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -4in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 4in\">Date</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{Witness Signature}</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -4in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 4in\">Witness&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb