(22,'Dr. Richard MacKool Eval','Dr. Richard MacKool Eval',9,'<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><b><u style=\"text-underline: double\">MEDICAL EVALUATION</u></b></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b><i>The Mackool Eye Institute</i></b></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b><i>31-27 41 Street</i></b></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b><i>Astoria, NY 11103</i></b></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 119%; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 119%\"><i><u>Surgical Office</u></i></span></b><span style=\"line-height: 119%\"> </span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 119%; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height: 119%\">Tel: (718)&nbsp;728-3400 Ext. 202, 203&nbsp;Fax: (718) 728-4882</span></i></b></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 119%; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height: 119%\">Attn: Veronica or Susan</span></i></b></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 119%; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 119%; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b>Subject: Request For Pre-Operative Tests for Minimally</b></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b>Invasive Surgery (Cataract or Anterior Segment Surgery)</b> </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\">Patient:{PATIENT FIRST NAME} {MIDDLE INITIAL} {LAST NAME}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\">Surgery Date:{TEXTBOX_MEDIUM}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\">Dear Doctor:</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller\">The above patient is scheduled for minimally invasive, elective eye surgery under local anesthesia with a licensed anesthesiologist caring for the patient at the Eye Institute, a free standing ambulatory surgery center. <b>The following is required and must be received at the Institute to the attention of the Surgical Office at least 5 days prior to surgery:</b></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: -1in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 1in\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b>History and Physical performed within 30 days of surgery and completion of the attached &ldquo;Patient History &amp; Physical&rdquo; </b></span><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b>form which includes &ldquo;Medications and Dosage&rdquo; required by NYS Department of Health.</b> </span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b>An EKG strip with interpretation within 1 year or less as you deem appropriate</b>. </span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><b>Any other tests, including lab tests deemed medically necessary by you.</b> If l