(32,'Attending YAG Medical Evaluation','Attending YAG Medical Evaluation',9,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><u>MEDICAL EVALUATION</u></b></div>\r\n<div><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b><i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The Mackool Eye Institute, LLC</i></b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b><i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 31-27 41 Street</i></b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b><i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Astoria, NY 11103</i></b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<b><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><b><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i><u>Surgical Office</u></i></span></b><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b><i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tel: (718) 721-6989<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Fax: (718) 728-0770</span></i></b></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b>Subject: Request For Pre-Operative Medical Evaluation for</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left\"><b><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; Yag laser procedure (a minimally invasive procedure)</span></b><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Patient:{PATIENT FIRST NAME} {MIDDLE INITIAL} {LAST NAME}</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Surgery Date: {DOS}</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Dear Doctor:</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>The above patient is scheduled for a Yag laser procedure of the eye with a topical anesthetic&nbsp;at The Mackool Eye Institute, LLC, an ambulatory surgery center.&nbsp;<b>The following is required by the federal government and must be received at the Institute to the attention of the Surgical Office at least 5 days prior to surgery:</b></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>\r\n<div><b><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; History and Physical performed within 30 days of procedure and completion of the attached &ldquo;Patient History &amp; Physical&rdquo; form which includes &ldquo;Medications &amp; Dosage&rdquo; required by NYS Department of Health.</span></b></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>If time does not permit mailing, please fax all of the above to the attention of the Surgical Scheduling Coordinator at <b>fax (718) 728-0770</b> and mail the originals.&nbsp;Your assistance with this mandated preoperative assessment is greatly appreciated.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Thank you.</di