action with an Intraocular Lens Implant. I do understand that this is not a guaranteed outcome, but that the doctor will aim to have this as a surgical result.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">Please make a check in the appropriate box:</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{TEXTBOX_XSMALL}I desire distance vision target (full correction). I may still be required to wear glasses for reading and distance, especially if I have astigmatism.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{TEXTBOX_XSMALL}I desire near vision target. I may still be required to wear glasses to see in the distance and reading, especially if I have astigmatism.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{TEXTBOX_XSMALL}I desire intermediate target (both eyes under/ over corrected) I realize I will need glasses for distance and near.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{TEXTBOX_XSMALL}I desire mono vision (dominant eye at distance, non-dominant eye at near or intermediate). I realize I may still need to wear glasses.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{TEXTBOX_XSMALL}I have corneal astigmatism and I desire to have it corrected with an astigmatism correcting<span> lens, I understand that this lens is not covered entirely by insurance and there will be an additional out of pocket cost. I realize I may still need to wear glasses.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{TEXTBOX_XSMALL}I desire to have a multifocal lens. I understand that this lens is not covered entirely by insurance and there will be an additional out of pocket cost. I realize I may still need to wear glasses</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{TEXTBOX_XSMALL}I have also been informed that if there is a medical reason that the chosen lens cannot be successfully implanted at the time of surgery, the surgeon will choose the lens implant that is appropriate for me.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{SIGNATURE}{DATE}{Witness Signature}</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">{LAST NAME} {MIDDLE INITIAL}{PATIENT FIRST NAME}{DOB}</div>','true'),
(50,'Advanced directive/ bill of rights','Advanced Directives/ bill of rights',20,'<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">Swagel Wootton Hiatt Eye Center</span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">CERTIFICATION THAT PATIENT HAS BEEN INFORMED OF THE RIGHT TO FORMULATE ADVANCE DIRECTIVES FOR HEALTH CARE</span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">PATIENT LABEL</span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">It is the policy of Swagel Wootton Eye Center, D.B.A. Eye Surgery Center of Arizona that because patients seen in our center are here for an elective procedure, we will not acknowledge a living will, health care power of attorney or advanced directives.</span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I certify that Swagel Wootton Eye Center has provided me information about the laws of Arizona and our facility\'s policies regarding my right to accept or refuse medical or surgical treatment and my right to formulate advanced directives for health care, such as a living will, a health care power of attorney or pre-hospital medical care directive. I will be provided the necessary forms to formulate advance directives, upon request.</span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">I have also read the policy of this facility regarding advanced directives and understand the policy.</span></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<