soothing and beneficial to the eye. If this is insufficient, please call the office.</li>\r\n    <li>Resume your normal routine. You may bend or stoop to do things such a tying your shoes or picking up a newspaper.</li>\r\n    <li>You may watch television or read.</li>\r\n    <li>Dr. Schumer will answer questions with regard to driving.</li>\r\n    <li>Resume your regular medications.</li>\r\n    <li>Whether you are inside or outside, you may be light-sensitive. You have been provided with sunglasses; wear them for eye comfort.</li>\r\n    <li>Your next appointment will be scheduled or confirmed as you leave the office with each visit.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>EYE DROPS: starting today when you get home:</strong></p>'),
