as slowly injected into the posterior </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.25in 0pt 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">capsular bag .The residual Viscoelastic material was removed with the I&amp;A tip.&nbsp;Balanced salt solution was</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.25in 0pt 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\"> injected into the eye to fill it to the normal pressure.&nbsp;The eye was tested by pressing on the eye and the incision </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.25in 0pt 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">was noted to be watertight.&nbsp;The chamber remained deep.&nbsp;One drop of Pilocarpine 2% was applied to the eye.&nbsp;Antibiotic ointment was applied.&nbsp;The patient was taken to the recovery area in good condition. </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.25in 0pt 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">{LAST NAME}{MIDDLE INITIAL}{PATIENT FIRST NAME}{DOB}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.25in 0pt 0in\">\r\n<p>{SURGEON NAME}{DOS}</p>\r\n</div>',311,0,0),
(79,'Cataract/ IFIS/ Healon','<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\">PREOPERATIVE DIAGNOSIS:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {PRE-OP DIAGNOSIS}, {SITE}</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; Alpha 1-adrenergic receptor antagonist use</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\">POSTOPERATIVE DIAGNOSIS:&nbsp; {POST-OP DIAGNOSIS},{SITE}</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Floppy iris syndrome</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\">OPERATIVE PROCEDURE:<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>{PROCEDURE}{SITE}</span></span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0in -0.25in 0pt 0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\">DESCRIPTION:</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\"> The patient was admitted to the surgery center.&nbs